FOR TEEN MOMS

21:55.480 --> 21:56.959
WHO DECIDE TO RAISE A CHILD.

21:57.100 --> 21:59.864
ADOPTION IS ALSO AN OPTION

22:00.000 --> 22:01.069
[fading out]
FOR YOU TO CONSIDER.

22:01.210 --> 22:03.519
NOW, IF YOU DECIDE
TO END THE PREGNANCY,

22:03.660 --> 22:04.934
YOU HAVE TWO OPTIONS...

22:05.080 --> 22:09.801
[man humming]

22:09.940 --> 22:12.420
