22:14.810 --> 22:18.018
- LATE IN THE NIGHT

22:18.160 --> 22:22.529
[students chattering
in background]

22:22.680 --> 22:24.955
- WELL, THERE'S ONLY...

22:25.100 --> 22:27.989
ONE OPTION, RIGHT?

22:28.130 --> 22:29.370
I MEAN, THE DOCTOR SAID
I COULD GET AN APPOINTMENT

22:29.520 --> 22:34.059
AS EARLY AS TOMORROW, SO--
- YEAH, YOU KNOW,

22:34.210 --> 22:37.247
