WOULD BE WILLING TO HELP US.

22:59.720 --> 23:02.120
AND I LOVE YOU,
AND THAT'S ALL THAT MATTERS.

23:05.310 --> 23:07.756
LOOK, OBVIOUSLY I'M GONNA
SUPPORT YOU NO MATTER WHAT.

23:07.900 --> 23:09.037
