THAT I'M NOT THERE FOR YOU

23:15.320 --> 23:18.733
IF YOU DECIDED TO KEEP IT,
THAT'S ALL.

23:22.710 --> 23:26.498
- I NEED HELP COMING UP
WITH THE MONEY.

23:28.330 --> 23:29.957
- OKAY.

