24:18.000 --> 24:19.649
- 'CAUSE HE'S GONNA GO TO
COLLEGE AND THAT'S NORMAL.

24:19.800 --> 24:21.449
I WAS FREAKING OUT MYSELF AND--

24:21.590 --> 24:25.105
BUT MARK, YOU KNOW,
I WAS JUST KIND OF THINKING--

24:25.250 --> 24:27.935
