WHAT YOU DID,
CALLING THE POLICE,

27:35.720 --> 27:39.304
WAS SERIOUS.

27:46.970 --> 27:47.959
- LISTEN TO YOUR MOM.

27:48.110 --> 27:50.271
- SHE'S NOT MY MOM.

28:01.050 --> 28:03.393
[door opens, closes]

28:03.540 --> 28:06.748
- OKAY, YOU KNOW WHAT?
THAT'S MY WIFE.

28:06.890 --> 28:08.027
DON'T TALK TO HER THAT WAY.

28:08.160 --> 28:10.128
- WHATEVER.
SHE DIDN'T EVEN GET ARRESTED.

28:10.270 --> 28:11.680
- VICTOR, DO YOU UNDERSTAND
WHAT YOU DID?

28:11.820 --> 28:13.879
YOU HAD THE POLICE
COME INTO OUR HOUSE.

28:14.030 --> 28:16.658
DO YOU UNDERSTAND THAT?

28:16.790 --> 28:19.486
IT REALLY HURT US.

28:19.620 --> 28:22.100
IT'S NOT ACCEPTABLE.

28:22.250 --> 28:25.276
AND YOU NEED
TO THINK ABOUT IT.

28:33.950 --> 28:35.178
- ANYWAY, WHEN YOU'RE
TAKING A SHOWER,

28:35.330 --> 28:37.013
THOSE ARE THE AREAS
YOU WANT TO FOCUS ON.

28:37.160 --> 28:39.196
