I WILL BEGIN TO SEE THEM

29:22.690 --> 29:24.920
IN A NEW AND EXCITING WAY.

29:26.100 --> 29:28.307
- WELL, THAT'S ONE WAY
OF PUTTING IT.

29:28.450 --> 29:30.486
- YEAH, BUT THAT'S
NOT GONNA HAPPEN WITH ME.

29:30.630 --> 29:34.100
- WELL, MAX, YOU SAY THAT NOW,
BUT TRUST ME, IT'S GONNA HAPPEN.

29:34.250 --> 29:39.734
WHEN I JUST, UH...WELL,
A LITTLE BIT OLDER THAN YOU,

29:39.880 --> 29:44.908
