JUST GIRLS TO...

29:45.050 --> 29:46.938
WELL, SOMETHING
NEW AND EXCITING.

29:47.090 --> 29:49.058
AND MYSTERIOUS.

29:49.200 --> 29:53.261
- BUT I'M NOT LIKE YOU,
BECAUSE I HAVE ASPERGER'S.

29:54.440 --> 29:58.024
- THAT IS TRUE.

29:58.170 --> 29:59.853
AND BECAUSE OF THAT,

30:00.000 --> 30:02.377
