31:48.490 --> 31:49.718
- YEAH, BIG DIFFERENCE THOUGH.

31:49.870 --> 31:51.906
I LIVED ON A BOAT,
SO IT WASN'T REALLY AN OPTION.

31:54.180 --> 31:55.283
- DO YOU HAVE ANY MORE CEREAL
BY ANY CHANCE?

31:55.430 --> 31:57.660
- NO, I THINK YOU ATE IT ALL,
ACTUALLY.

