32:18.590 --> 32:21.445
[engine turns off]
- THANKS FOR DRIVING ME.

32:21.590 --> 32:24.241
- YEAH, UM...

32:24.390 --> 32:26.312
I'LL JUST CALL YOU LATER?

32:31.840 --> 32:33.831
- MAYBE YOU SHOULDN'T.

32:33.980 --> 32:36.949
I NEED SOME SPACE.

32:39.300 --> 32:42.224
- OKAY.
HOW MUCH SPACE?

32:43.650 --> 32:48.121
- [sighs]
A LOT.

32:48.270 --> 32:52.513
- YEAH.
ALL RIGHT, OKAY.

32:56.070 --> 33:00.006
- OKAY, WELL, MY DAD'S HOME,
SO...

